title: Does a Pixel 2 XL G011B exist?
content:
I ordered a replacement battery but got a battery for a "Google Pixel 2 XL B011B and B011B-B" but I can't find any official Google Pixel phone that has this name? Only G011A for the smaller Pixel 2 and G011C for the bigger Pixel 2 XL.

Did I get scammed?
